From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: experintellia <280144245+experintellia@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 6 Jul 2026 00:57:11 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 03/11] wasm: stub HTTP/proxy modules, rustls ring provider

- net/http_wasm.rs, net/proxy_wasm.rs: compile-compatible stubs selected
  via #[cfg]+#[path]; every operation errors at runtime (fetch()/WS proxy
  is the upgrade path)
- tls: default_provider() helper -> aws-lc-rs native, ring on wasm;
  non-strict TLS falls back to rustls (no native-tls on wasm)
- session: gate native-tls/socks5/shadowsocks SessionStream impls
- qr: shadowsocks QR decoding errors on wasm
---
 src/net.rs            |  8 +++++
 src/net/http_wasm.rs  | 75 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/net/proxy_wasm.rs | 45 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/net/session.rs    |  4 +++
 src/net/tls.rs        | 65 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++----------
 src/net/tls/danger.rs |  8 ++---
 src/qr.rs             |  7 ++++
 7 files changed, 191 insertions(+), 21 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 src/net/http_wasm.rs
 create mode 100644 src/net/proxy_wasm.rs

